column5: Was lucky enough to get out with Brian. Marked a pile if fish, sadly no takers for either of us on Saturday. But I learned a bit more and met 2 OFC legends! Brian and Terry, So, I'm calling the day a success! Thanks again guys!!!!
It was good to meet you
Good to meet ya Sheldon. Keep at it. Once you get your first, they will come. We are into the feb blahhhhs. Towards the end of the month, it will pick up.
Now you know what, RIP and DEAD STICK means. LOL''And your smitty creation was top notch. Nice build.
